Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這 這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這是透姐做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎怎怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你問我我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.91,0:01:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才都怪庖姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 難道是我的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.45,0:01:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,比 比起那個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,快躲起來
Comment: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:47.67,Name,,0,0,0,,#桑名江
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.57,0:01:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,庖丁她們是怎麼了
Comment: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:52.42,Name,,0,0,0,,#牛王吉光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是花粉症
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:10.23,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\pos(1060,356)\alpha&H80&\3c&H77AAFF&\3a&H70&}庖丁三姐妹「喧鬧的每日」
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.27,0:02:10.23,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\pos(1060,356)}庖丁三姐妹「喧鬧的每日」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 這是怎麼回事
Comment: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:18.37,Name,,0,0,0,,#城和泉正宗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,突然就碎了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.85,0:02:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我們的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,反正都是你們引起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好了好了 城和泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她們也沒有惡意的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那這算什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:42.47,Screen2,,0,0,0,,花粉性黃色藥品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,大概這就是秋天的花粉症吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:03:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,或許連巫劍都無法抵擋花粉的威力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 牛王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,今天還怎麼營業啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:15.97,Screen2,,0,0,0,,今日停業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,下次也要看喔！
